data.text:
The easiest way to run GIMP on Android.

Features:

Full featured GIMP

Runs locally on your device

Touch based interface for interacting with GIMP

You can see our templates by visiting our issue center.

This app is released under the GPLv3. The source code can be found here. The icon, Wilber, the GIMP mascot, comes from a vector image source (SVG) made available by Jakub Steiner, available as Creative Commons by-sa 3.0. This app is not created by the main GIMP development team. Instead it is an adaptation that allows the Linux version to run on Android.
